attributes.description: Overview of Microsoft Defender XDR Alert Events.

params.markdown:
**Overview**

This dashboard visualizes Alert type events according to the [Microsoft Documentation](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/defender-xdr/advanced-hunting-deviceevents-table?view=o365-worldwide).  
The data is collected from a configured Event Hub, using the Microsoft Defender XDR Event datastream.

The supported event types are:
- AdvancedHunting-AlertEvidence
- AdvancedHunting-AlertInfo

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/m365_defender/overview)**
